OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy start, with
OL,6,Fblustery showers, although some
OL,7,Fbrighter spells in the east. Some
OL,8,Fsunny spells developing in the
OL,9,Fafternoon, with showers becoming
OL,10,Fconfined to the west. Feeling warm in
OL,11,Fany afternoon sunshine, but this
OL,12,Ftempered by strong winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers and wind easing this
OL,15,Fevening with some sunny spells. Cloud
OL,16,Fthickening overnight, with rain
OL,17,Farriving before dawn. Wind
OL,18,Fstrengthening a little again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
