OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy, damp and breezy but
OL,6,Fwarm. Rain may be heavy in the
OL,7,Fmorning, but will tend to ease,
OL,8,Fbecoming mostly dry later. Some
OL,9,Fbrightness possible in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMuch
OL,12,Fwarmer during this period. Friday,
OL,13,Fwarm or very warm with hazy sunshine.
OL,14,FSaturday remaining warm with sunny
OL,15,Fspells. Perhaps more cloudy with rain
OL,16,Flater Sunday, but still warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
